 - be level 40 or more,<br>
 - like raids and challenges,<br>
 - like to play in a family and help others,<br>
 - have a sponsor in the guild,<br>
<br>
 Then you can post on this board, contact a recruitment officer in game (Bracchus, Dumak or Tkachuk), or send a mail to TavernHeroes@hotmail.com.<br>
 <br>
 <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>         Be an Applicant</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
 During 1 week or 2 you will be consider as an applicant.<br>
 You will be able to follow the guild in all the raids or groups.<br>
 Your parain or someone else will tell you and inform you of what happen.<br>
 We do a lot of guild groups every weeks to help someone, to visit a place or just to do Xp.<br>
 At the end of this period the officers will discuss with the persons who know you and you may be interviewed by our Guild Leader.<br>
 Then you will be invited in the guild.<br>
<br>
 <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>         Be an Initiate</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
 This is a period of 1 or 2 weeks, you have the guild tag and you have access to the private board.<br>
 During this period all the officer will try to know you and will discuss with your sponsor.<br>
 You will participate to raids and guild events but you will be out of the lotto.<br>
 Then the officers will discuss about you and approve you as full member or not.<br>
<br>
 <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>         What can make the process faster?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
 We know you since a long time and you already did a lot of raids with us in the past.<br>
 You are a class we need particulary, then we'll try to evaluate you faster.<br>
 The current class Tavern Heroes needs.<br>
<br>
 Also during the Applicant and the Initiate period the more we see you the faster you will be integrate in the guild.<br>
<br>
 <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>       Tavern Heroes needs are:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
